<p>The CEO had big visions for our Head Quarters. He wanted the room to serve as both the MOC and the place to show off our software during demonstrations. I was told the interfaces he envisioned were interactive with (?? word for kinect/VR type interaction ?? gesture recognition with optical sensors) in one area, and dark-board type operations overviews across the rest of the screens. </p>
<br>
<br>
<p>I put together ideas to meet these specifications, and rendered a 3D model in Google Sketchup with list of materials to show it was obtainable within budget. </p>
